### 相关系数矩阵可视化 {#sec-correlation-matrix}




::: {.cell layout-align="center"}

```{.r .cell-code}
library(corrplot)

# 计算相关系数矩阵
cor_matrix <- cor(cor_data, method = "spearman")

# 创建相关系数矩阵图
corrplot(cor_matrix,
         method = "color",
         type = "upper",
         addCoef.col = "black",
         tl.col = "black",
         tl.srt = 45,
         diag = FALSE)
